      "writtenOn": "2026-07-14T19:52:19Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "LocationCode exists on both PCIeDevice service and PCIeSlot service. I confirmed this with the following commands:\n/tmp# busctl get-property xyz.openbmc_project.Inventory.Manager \\\n\u003e   /xyz/openbmc_project/inventory/system/chassis/motherboard/pcieslot2 \\\n\u003e   xyz.openbmc_project.Inventory.Decorator.LocationCode LocationCode\ns \"U78DA.N00.1234567-P0-C2\"\n\nbusctl get-property xyz.openbmc_project.Inventory.Manager \\\n\u003e   /xyz/openbmc_project/inventory/system/chassis/motherboard/pcieslot2/pcie_card2 \\\n\u003e   xyz.openbmc_project.Inventory.Decorator.LocationCode LocationCode\ns \"U78DA.N00.1234567-P0-C2\"",
